    <text type="letter">
        <body>
            <pb xml:id="leaf001r" facs="loc_jc.00424_large.jpg" type="recto"/>
            <opener>
                <dateline>
                    <date when="1878-01-26" rend="right">Saturday <choice><abbr>Jan</abbr><expan>January</expan></choice> 26 1878</date>
                </dateline>
                <salute>Dear friend</salute>
            </opener>

            <p>I write again <choice><sic>fore</sic><corr>for</corr></choice> you to come down we all want to see you so much.<ptr target="n0817"/> George<ptr target="n0852b"/> is not able to do <choice><orig>any thing</orig><reg>anything</reg></choice> &amp; he wants you to come to talk to him &amp; Cheer him up we shall send to the Station for you Tuesday 29<hi rend="superscript">th</hi> <choice><sic>besure</sic><corr>be sure</corr></choice> &amp; come on the 4 pm train</p>
            
            <closer>
                <salute>yours with love</salute>
                <signed>S. M. Stafford</signed>
            </closer>
            
            <postscript><p><unclear reason="damage" cert="medium" resp="#vm">do not disappoint us fore we shall send</unclear> <gap reason="damage" extent="2 or 3 words" quantity="7" unit="chars"/> you Tuesday</p></postscript>
            
